  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a sorcerer, you gain the following class features.</p>\n<h5>Hit Points</h5>\n<p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d6 per sorcerer level</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 16 + your Constitution modifier</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d6 (or 4) + your Constitution modifier per sorcerer level after 1st</p>\n<h5>Proficiencies</h5>\n<p><strong>Armor:</strong> None</p>\n<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Daggers, darts, slings, quarterstaffs, light crossbows</p>\n<p><strong>Tools:</strong> None</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Constitution, Charisma</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose two from Arcana, Deception, Insight, Intimidation, Persuasion, and Religion</p>\n<h5>Equipment</h5>\n<p>You start one of the following equipment options, in addition to the equipment granted by your background:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>An arcane focus, a dagger, a light crossbow with 20 bolts, a traveler's pack, and 40 gp</li>\n<li>100 gp worth of equipment, and an equipment pack</li>\n</ul>",
